@node part1 "What is it?"



            Calculator is unsurprisingly - a calculator. It performs all
            of the functions of an ordinary calculator.
            It also performs some more advanced functions.

            To discover why I created Calculator click @{"here" link part5}.

            If you want to run it you'll want to know the @{"system requirements" link part2}.

            Or jump straight to @{"usage" link part4} for instructions on
            how to access the program.


                        @{"Return to contents" link main}
@endnode

